No subject line. No JSON. No markdown. No placeholders.

Use these exact values in your email:
- Origin: {{ $json.origin }}
- Destination: {{ $json.destination }}
- Total Rate: ${{ $json.sell_rate }}
- Transit Time: {{ $json.transit_days }} business days
- Pickup Date: {{ $json.pickup_date }}
- Quote Reference: {{ $json.quote_id }}
- Quote valid for 4 hours

Tone: Professional, confident, brief — 4 to 6 sentences.
End with: To confirm, please reply APPROVED to this email.
Sign off as: AMZ Prep Logistics Team
Do NOT reveal carrier name or our cost.

